      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54B32 high-pressure 3.2L inline-six engine. This example is an enthusiast-spec build with the factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS refresh and rod bearing replacement to ensure internal longevity. The chassis has been",
