    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a truly dependable and well-presented vehicle that has served as a reliable daily driver. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep, reflective gloss; while there are a few minor pea-sized stone chips on the lower front valance and a small, faint scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, the body remains straight and free of any major dents or rust. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight. The charcoal leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display\u2014including the navigation and heated seats\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and I recently invested in a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires and new ceramic brake pads. The engine pulls smoothly without hesitation, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that comes with a complete set of service records and two key fobs. This is an honest, high-quality car ready for its next chapter.",
