    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and exhibits the crisp throttle response inherent to its individual throttle body setup. The 6-speed Getrag transmission shifts with precision, and the mechanical limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load. Critically, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure timing stability at the 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension geometry is dialed in with refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative chassis dynamics this platform is known for. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals and structural integrity are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the purist who values turn-key performance.",
